4.6 Option for command prompt styles
====================================

Symbol names:

   • ‘modus-operandi-theme-prompts’
   • ‘modus-vivendi-theme-prompts’

   Possible values:

  1. ‘nil’ (default)
  2. ‘subtle’
  3. ‘intense’

   The symbols “subtle” and “intense” will apply a combination of
